function hex2rgb(hex) hex = hex:gsub("#","") return {r=tonumber("0x"..hex:sub(1,2)), g=tonumber("0x"..hex:sub(3,4)), b=tonumber("0x"..hex:sub(5,6))} end
function onTick() H=(((1-input.getNumber(1))%1)*360) C=hex2rgb(property.getText("Bars Color (Hex)")) C2=hex2rgb(property.getText("Heading Color (Hex)")) T=property.getNumber("Bars Transparency") OF=property.getNumber("Height Offset") FLP=property.getBool("Flip Vertically") Show=property.getBool("Show Heading") end
function onDraw() w=screen.getWidth() h=screen.getHeight()
sp=H-math.floor(H/5)*5 l=math.ceil((w/2-sp)/5) x=w/2-sp-l*5 v=math.floor(H-w/2+x)%360
if FLP == true then PL = -6 P1 = 1 P2 = 0 else PL = 3 P1 = 0 P2 = 1 end
screen.setColor(C["r"],C["g"],C["b"],T) while (x<w) do if (v/15==math.floor(v/15)) then screen.drawLine(x, OF, x, 2+OF) if x<w/2-12 or x>w/2+12 or Show == false then if v==0 then screen.drawText(x-1,PL+OF,"N") elseif v==45 then screen.drawText(x-4,PL+OF,"NE") elseif v==90 then screen.drawText(x-1,PL+OF,"E") elseif v==135 then screen.drawText(x-4,PL+OF,"SE") elseif v==180 then screen.drawText(x-1,PL+OF,"S") elseif v==225 then screen.drawText(x-4,PL+OF,"SW") elseif v==270 then screen.drawText(x-1,PL+OF,"W") elseif v==315 then screen.drawText(x-4,PL+OF,"NW") end end else screen.drawLine(x, P1+OF, x, P2+OF) end x=x+5 v=(v+5)%360 end if Show == true then screen.setColor(C2["r"],C2["g"],C2["b"]) screen.drawLine(w/2, OF, w/2, 2+OF) screen.drawText((w-#(string.format("%.0f", H))*5)/2+1, PL+OF, string.format("%.0f", H)) end end

object.script:
si=math.sin co=math.cos pi=math.pi pi2=pi*2 s=screen ip=input
mx=gpsx my=gpsy zoom=0.5 zoomScale=zoom+zoom focusZone=false grid=250
function onTick() rx=ip.getNumber(1) ry=ip.getNumber(2) inputX=ip.getNumber(3) inputY=ip.getNumber(4) pressed=ip.getBool(1) and not isPressed--pulse isPressed=ip.getBool(1)
gpsx=ip.getNumber(10) gpsy=ip.getNumber(11)
compass=ip.getNumber(12)*pi2*-1 alt=ip.getNumber(13) if alt<0 then alt=0 end
zoomingIn=isPressed and iPIR(inputX,inputY,0,ry/5,6,ry/5) zoomingOut=isPressed and iPIR(inputX,inputY,0,ry/5*2,6,ry/5) reset=isPressed and iPIR(inputX,inputY,0,ry/5*3,6,ry/5)
if reset then focusZone=false zoom=1.5 grid=250 end if isPressed and inputX>6 then focusZone=true end if focusZone then if pressed and inputX>6 then tx,ty=map.screenToMap(mx,my,zoom,rx,ry,inputX,inputY) end cx,cy=map.screenToMap(mx,my,zoom,rx,ry,rx/2,ry/2) mx=cx+((tx-cx)*0.05) my=cy+((ty-cy)*0.05) else mx=gpsx my=gpsy end if zoomingIn and zoom>0.1 then zoomScale=zoom+zoom zoom=zoom-(zoomScale/100) end if zoomingOut and zoom<50 then zoomScale=zoom+zoom zoom=zoom+(zoomScale/100) end if zoom>0 and zoom<0.2 then grid=25 end if zoom>0.2 and zoom<0.5 then grid=50 end if zoom>0.5 and zoom<1 then grid=100 end if zoom>1 and zoom<2 then grid=250 end if zoom>2 and zoom<5 then grid=500 end if zoom>5 and zoom<10 then grid=1000 end if zoom>10 and zoom<20 then grid=2000 end if zoom>20 and zoom<40 then grid=4000 end if zoom>40 then grid=8000 end end function onDraw() w=s.getWidth() h=s.getHeight()
s.drawMap(mx,my+alt,zoom) s.setMapColorOcean(10,10,15) s.setMapColorShallows(15,15,20) s.setMapColorLand(60,60,60) s.setMapColorGrass(40,60,40) s.setMapColorSand(55,55,50) s.setMapColorSnow(80,80,80)
x1,y1=map.screenToMap(mx,my+alt,zoom,w,h,0,0) x2,y2=map.screenToMap(mx,my+alt,zoom,w,h,w,h) x1=math.floor(x1/grid)*grid y1=math.floor(y1/grid)*grid
s.setColor(0,100,15,20) for xx=x1,x2,grid do x,y = map.mapToScreen(mx,my+alt,zoom,w,h,xx,y1) screen.drawLine(x,0,x,h) end for yy=y1,y2,-grid do x,y = map.mapToScreen(mx,my+alt,zoom,w,h,x1,yy) screen.drawLine(0,y,w,y) end
dpsx,dpsy=map.mapToScreen(mx,my+alt,zoom,w,h,gpsx,gpsy) dpx,dpy=map.mapToScreen(mx,my,zoom,w,h,gpsx,gpsy) s.setColor(0,0,0,150) drawPointer(dpsx,dpsy+1,10,compass)--shadow s.setColor(255,255,255,60) s.drawLine(dpsx,dpsy,dpx,dpy)--line s.setColor(255,255,255) drawPointer(dpx,dpy,10,compass)
s.setColor(0,0,0,150) s.drawRectF(0,h/5,6,h/5*3)
if zoomingIn then s.setColor(0,100,15,255) else s.setColor(0,100,15,60)end s.drawTextBox(1,h/5,4,h/5,"+",0,0) if zoomingOut then s.setColor(0,100,15,255) else s.setColor(0,100,15,60)end s.drawTextBox(1,h/5*2,4,h/5,"-",0,0) if reset then s.setColor(0,100,15,255) else s.setColor(0,100,15,60)end s.drawTextBox(1,h/5*3,4,h/5,"r",0,0)
if not focusZone then if w>100 then s.setColor(0,0,0,150) s.drawLine(dpsx-6,dpsy-5,dpsx-10,dpsy-9) s.drawLine(dpsx+6,dpsy-5,dpsx+10,dpsy-9) s.drawLine(dpsx+6,dpsy+6,dpsx+10,dpsy+10) s.drawLine(dpsx-6,dpsy+6,dpsx-10,dpsy+10) s.setColor(255,255,255) s.drawLine(w/2-6,h/2-6,w/2-10,h/2-10) s.drawLine(w/2+6,h/2-6,w/2+10,h/2-10) s.drawLine(w/2+6,h/2+5,w/2+10,h/2+9) s.drawLine(w/2-6,h/2+5,w/2-10,h/2+9) end else x=dpx y=dpy L=h/6 s.setColor(255,255,255) s.drawRectF(w/2,h/2,1,1) if not iPIR(x,y,0,0,w,h) then x,y = w/2-x,h/2-y v = math.sqrt((x^2)+(y^2)) x,y = x/v,y/v s.drawLine(w/2-x*2,h/2-y*2-1,w/2-x*L,h/2-y*L-1) end end
--s.setColor(0,100,15,60) --s.drawRect(6,0,w-7,h-1) end
function iPIR(x,y,rX,rY,rW,rH) return x>rX and y>rY and x<rX+rW and y<rY+rH end function drawPointer(x,y,s,r,...) a=... a=(a or 30)*pi/360 x=x+s/2*si(r) y=y-s/2*co(r) screen.drawTriangleF(x,y,x-s*si(r+a),y+s*co(r+a),x-s*si(r-a),y+s*co(r-a)) end

object.script:
VSI = 0 strUnit = "" intVSI = 0 acc = {} for i = 1, math.max(1, property.getNumber("Lag")) do acc[i] = 0 end
function onTick() for i = 1, #acc -1 do acc[i] = acc[i+1] end acc[#acc] = input.getNumber(32)
VSI = 0 for i = 1, #acc do VSI = VSI + acc[i] end VSI = VSI / #acc
Unit_Type = property.getNumber("UNIT") if Unit_Type == 1 then intVSI = VSI * 3.28084 * 60 / 1000 VSI = VSI * 3.28084 *60 / 2000 strUnit = "x1000ft/m" elseif Unit_Type == 2 then intVSI = VSI / 10 VSI = VSI / 20 strUnit = "x10m/s" end VSI = math.max(VSI, -1) VSI = math.min(VSI, 1) end
-- Draw function that will be executed when this script renders to a screen function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() -- Get the screen's width and height h = screen.getHeight() screen.setColor(0, 0, 0, 255) screen.drawClear()
if w > 32 and false then screen.setColor(160, 160, 160, 255) screen.drawTextBox(0, 8, w, 5, "ALT", 0, -1) screen.drawTextBox(0, 24, w, 5, strUnit, 0, 1) end screen.setColor(200, 200, 200, 255)
rMark(math.pi * -0.3, 6) --2 rMark(math.pi * -0.1, 3) --1.5 rMark(math.pi * 0.1, 6) --1 rMark(math.pi * 0.3, 3) --0.5 rMark(math.pi * 0.5, 6) --0 rMark(math.pi * 0.7, 3) -- -0.5 rMark(math.pi * 0.9, 6) -- -1 rMark(math.pi * 1.1, 3) -- -1.5 rMark(math.pi * 1.3, 6) -- -2
--VSI value: screen.drawTextBox(0, h/2 -2, w, 5, string.format("%.0f", intVSI), 1, 1)
AHand(VSI,16,5)
screen.drawCircleF(w/2, h/2, 3) --screen.setColor(0, 0, 0, 255) --screen.drawCircleF(w/2, h/2, 2) --screen.setColor(0, 200, 0, 255) --screen.drawTextBox(0, 0, w, 5, "H="..H, -1, -1) --screen.drawTextBox(0, 6, w, 5, "M="..M, -1, -1) --screen.drawTextBox(0, 12, w, 5, "S="..S, -1, -1) end
function rMark(deg, length) screen.drawLine(w/2 - w/2 * math.sin(deg), h/2 - h/2 * math.cos(deg), w/2 - (w/2 - length) * math.sin(deg), h/2 - (h/2 - length) * math.cos(deg)) end
function AHand(ALT,length,width) local deg = -math.pi * (0.5 - ALT *4/5) width = width/2 screen.drawTriangleF(w/2 + length * math.sin(deg), h/2 - length * math.cos(deg), w/2 - width * math.cos(deg), h/2 - width * math.sin(deg), w/2 + width * math.cos(deg), h/2 + width * math.sin(deg)) end

function hex2rgb(hex) hex = hex:gsub("#","") return {r=tonumber("0x"..hex:sub(1,2)), g=tonumber("0x"..hex:sub(3,4)), b=tonumber("0x"..hex:sub(5,6))} end
function onTick() p = inp.getBool(1) x = inp.getNumber(3) y = inp.getNumber(4) str = inp.getNumber(5) recv = inp.getBool(3) out.setNumber(1,freq) out.setBool(1,ptt)
BGC = hex2rgb(property.getText("Background Color (Hex)")) FGC = hex2rgb(property.getText("Foreground Color (Hex)")) end function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() h = screen.getHeight()
sc.setColor(BGC["r"],BGC["g"],BGC["b"],255) sc.drawClear() sc.setColor(FGC["r"]*0.3,FGC["g"]*0.3,FGC["b"]*0.3,255) if y > 24 then if x < 10 and p then sc.drawRectF(4,25,6,10) if freq > 1 then freq=freqb-1 end elseif x > 10 and x < 17 and p then sc.drawRectF(10,25,6,10) if freq < 88 then freq=freqb+1 end else freqb=freq end if x > 16 and p then sc.drawRectF(16,25,16,8) ptt=true else ptt=false end end if recv then sc.setColor(FGC["r"],FGC["g"],FGC["b"],255) else sc.setColor(FGC["r"]*0.1,FGC["g"]*0.1,FGC["b"]*0.1,255) end sc.drawText(7,10,"I") sc.drawText(10,10,"NCOM")
sx = 19 sy = -9 sc.setColor(FGC["r"]*0.1,FGC["g"]*0.1,FGC["b"]*0.1,255) if str > 0.8 then sc.setColor(FGC["r"],FGC["g"],FGC["b"],255) end sc.drawRectF(10+sx,10+sy,1,5) if str > 0.65 then sc.setColor(FGC["r"],FGC["g"],FGC["b"],255) end sc.drawRectF(8+sx,11+sy,1,4) if str > 0.35 then sc.setColor(FGC["r"],FGC["g"],FGC["b"],255) end sc.drawRectF(6+sx,12+sy,1,3) if str > 0.1 then sc.setColor(FGC["r"],FGC["g"],FGC["b"],255) end sc.drawRectF(4+sx,13+sy,1,2)
sc.setColor(FGC["r"],FGC["g"],FGC["b"],255) sc.drawLine(0,24,w,24) sc.drawLine(0,7,w,7) sc.drawLine(10,25,10,32) sc.drawLine(16,25,16,32) sc.drawText(6,26,"-") sc.drawText(12,26,"+") sc.drawText(18,26,"PT") sc.drawText(27,26,"T") sc.drawText(8,17,"CH:") sc.drawText(21,17,string.format("%.0f",freq)) sc.drawText(7,1,"V") sc.drawText(11,1,"HF") end

object.script:
tilt = 0 rollAngle = 0 vertCheck = true lineDist = property.getNumber('Degrees per Line') pixPerDegree = property.getNumber('Pixels per Degree') maxLineWidth = property.getNumber('Maximum Line Length as Screen Percent') lineDivideFactor = (property.getNumber('Minimum Line Length as Percent of Max')+1)*90 if property.getBool('Vertical Flip') then yMod = -1 else yMod = 1 end
function onTick() tilt = input.getNumber(1)*360 -- Tilt (Forward tilt sensor) supplied through composite 1 maxAngle = 90-math.abs(tilt) rollAngle = (input.getNumber(2)*360)/maxAngle*90 -- Roll (Right tilt sensor) supplied through composite 2 vertCheck = input.getNumber(3)>=0 if not vertCheck then -- Vertical check (Up tilt sensor) supplied through composite 3 tilt = tilt*-1 rollAngle = rollAngle*-1 end SpeedKTS=input.getNumber(11) SpeedKPH=input.getNumber(13) H5=input.getBool(5) DBK=input.getNumber(12)
B32=input.getBool(32) H22=input.getBool(4) ID=input.getNumber(20) end
function calcXY(x,y,bearing,distance) bearing = math.rad(bearing + 90) y = y+math.cos(bearing) * -distance x = x+math.sin(bearing) * distance return x,y end
function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() h = screen.getHeight()
if vertCheck then screen.setColor(100,50,0,150) else screen.setColor(50,50,255,150) end for lineAngle = -90, 90, lineDist do if lineAngle>0 and vertCheck then screen.setColor(50,50,255,150) elseif lineAngle>0 and not vertCheck then screen.setColor(100,50,0,150) end lineLen = (maxLineWidth*w)*(1-math.abs(lineAngle)/lineDivideFactor) currentY = (tilt-lineAngle)*pixPerDegree*yMod mX, mY = calcXY(w/2,h/2,rollAngle+90,currentY) lX, lY = calcXY(mX,mY,rollAngle,lineLen/2) rX, rY = calcXY(mX,mY,rollAngle+180,lineLen/2) screen.drawLine(lX,lY,rX,rY) end centerY = h/2+tilt*pixPerDegree*yMod screen.setColor(125,125,125,150) mX, mY = calcXY(w/2,h/2,rollAngle+90,tilt*pixPerDegree*yMod) lX, lY = calcXY(mX,mY,rollAngle,100) rX, rY = calcXY(mX,mY,rollAngle+180,100) screen.drawLine(lX,lY,rX,rY) screen.setColor(255,0,0,180) screen.drawRectF(w/2-1,h/2,2,2)
screen.setColor(255,255,255,130) screen.drawText(w-16,4,"DBK") screen.setColor(255,255,255,200) screen.drawText(w-23,11,string.format("%03.0f",DBK)) screen.drawText(w-6,11,"m")
if B32 and ID==15 then if H22 then screen.setColor(0,255,0,130)else screen.setColor(255,255,255,130)end screen.drawText(w-95,h-23,"SPEED") if H22 then screen.setColor(0,255,0,200)else screen.setColor(255,255,255,200)end screen.drawText(w-95,h-17,string.format("%03.0f",SpeedKPH))screen.drawText(w-78,h-17,"kph") else if H5 then screen.setColor(0,255,0,130)else screen.setColor(255,255,255,130)end screen.drawText(w-95,h-23,"SPEED") if H5 then screen.setColor(0,255,0,200)else screen.setColor(255,255,255,200)end screen.drawText(w-95,h-17,string.format("%03.0f",SpeedKTS))screen.drawText(w-78,h-17,"kt")screen.drawText(w-69,h-17,"s") end
end

object.script:
--SETTINGS-- enableNightVision="1" -- For disable nightvision, write a number higther then 1 / For activate : write 1 isGimble="1" -- for disable movement buttons, write a number highter then 1 enableResetBtn="1" -- for disable reset button, write a number highter then 1
presetPitch={val=0.764, min=-1, max=1} presetRot={val=0, min=-1, max=1} presetZoom={val=0.54, min=0, max=1}
--DO NOT TOUCH-- pitch=0 rot=0 zoom=0 nv=false
dG="0"
buttonsCount=10 btn={ {name="showMenu", grp="0", toggle=true, pos={x=1, y=1, w=11, h=11}, c=function() screen.drawCircle(6, 5, 3) end, cB=function() dG="1" states[2].active=false end}, {name="hideMenu", grp="1", toggle=true, pos={x=1, y=1, w=11, h=11}, c=function() screen.drawCircle(6, 5, 3) screen.drawLine(10, 1, 1, 10) end, cB=function() dG="0" states[1].active=false end}, {name="leftMove", grp=isGimble, toggle=false, pos={x=13, y=1, w=10, h=10}, c=function() screen.drawTriangleF(21, 2, 21, 10, 15, 6) end, cB=function() rot=rot+0.01 end}, {name="rightMove", grp=isGimble, toggle=false, pos={x=22, y=1, w=10, h=10}, c=function() screen.drawTriangleF(24, 2, 24, 10, 30, 6) end, cB=function() rot=rot-0.01 end}, {name="upMove", grp=isGimble, toggle=false, pos={x=31, y=1, w=10, h=10}, c=function() screen.drawTriangleF(33, 9, 39, 9, 36, 2) end, cB=function() pitch=pitch+0.01 end}, {name="downMove", grp=isGimble, toggle=false, pos={x=40, y=1, w=10, h=10}, c=function() screen.drawTriangleF(41, 2, 48, 2, 45, 10) end, cB=function() pitch=pitch-0.01 end}, {name="resetPos", grp=isGimble, toggle=false, pos={x=49, y=1, w=10, h=10}, c=function() screen.drawTextBox(50, 2, 8, 8, "R", 0, 0) end, cB=function() pitch=presetPitch.val rot=presetRot.val zoom=presetZoom.val end}, {name="upZoom", grp="1", toggle=false, pos={x=1, y=13, w=10, h=10}, c=function() screen.drawTextBox(2, 14, 8, 8, "+", 0, 0) end, cB=function() zoom=zoom+0.01 end}, {name="downZoom", grp="1", toggle=false, pos={x=1, y=22, w=10, h=10}, c=function() screen.drawTextBox(2, 24, 8, 8, "-", 0, 0) end, cB=function() zoom=zoom-0.01 end}, {name="nightVision", toggle=true, grp=enableNightVision, pos={x=1, y=37, w=10, h=10}, c=function() screen.drawTextBox(2, 38, 8, 8, "N", 0, 0) end, cB=function() nv=not nv end} } states={} function init() pitch=presetPitch.val rot=presetRot.val zoom=presetZoom.val for i=1, buttonsCount do states[i] = {active=true, count=0} end end init() function cooldown() for i=1, buttonsCount do if states[i].active == false then states[i].count=states[i].count+1 end if states[i].count >= 30 then states[i].active=true states[i].count=0 end end end function touchPad(tX, tY, tZ) if tZ == true then for i=1, buttonsCount do if btn[i].grp == dG and states[i].active == true then if tX >= btn[i].pos.x and tX <= btn[i].pos.x+btn[i].pos.w then if tY >= btn[i].pos.y and tY <= btn[i].pos.y+btn[i].pos.h then btn[i].cB() if btn[i].toggle == true then states[i].active=false end end end end end end end function onTick() tX = input.getNumber(3) tY = input.getNumber(4) tZ = input.getBool(1) touchPad(tX, tY, tZ) output.setNumber(1, pitch) output.setNumber(2, rot) output.setNumber(3, zoom) output.setBool(4, nv) cooldown() if pitch <= presetPitch.min then pitch=presetPitch.min elseif pitch >= presetPitch.max then pitch=presetPitch.max elseif rot <= presetRot.min then rot=presetRot.min elseif rot >= presetRot.max then rot=presetRot.max elseif zoom <= presetZoom.min then zoom=presetZoom.min elseif zoom >= presetZoom.max then zoom=presetZoom.max end end function onDraw() w = screen.getWidth() h = screen.getHeight() for i=1, buttonsCount do if btn[i].grp == dG then screen.setColor(10,10,10) screen.drawRectF(btn[i].pos.x, btn[i].pos.y, btn[i].pos.w, btn[i].pos.h-1) screen.setColor(200,200,200) screen.drawRectF(btn[i].pos.x+1, btn[i].pos.y, btn[i].pos.w-2, btn[i].pos.h-1) screen.setColor(10,10,10) btn[i].c() end end end

function onTick() text = input.getNumber(12) inputX = input.getNumber(3) inputY = input.getNumber(4) isPressed = input.getBool(1) auto1 = input.getBool(24) output.setBool(2, rdown) output.setBool(17, rup) output.setBool(20, zoomin) output.setBool(21, zoomout) output.setBool(22, auto) text1 = input.getNumber(25) rdown = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, 6, 1, 4, 4) rup = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, 6, 5, 4, 4) if auto1 == false then zoomin = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, 26, 7, 4, 4) end if auto1 == false then zoomout = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, 26, 20, 4, 4) end auto = isPressed and isPointInRectangle(inputX, inputY, 26, 13, 7, 7) end function isPointInRectangle(x, y, rectX, rectY, rectW, rectH) return x > rectX and y > rectY and x < rectX+rectW and y < rectY+rectH end
function onDraw() screen.setColor(0,100,15,255) if text < 10 then screen.drawText(27, 1, text)elseif text < 100 then screen.drawText(22, 1, text)else screen.drawText(17, 1, text) end if auto1 then screen.setColor(0,100,15,255) screen.drawRectF(26,13,7,7) end if auto1 then screen.setColor(0,0,0) screen.drawText(27, 14, "A") else screen.setColor(0,100,15,39,90) screen.drawText(27, 14, "A") end screen.setColor(0,100,15,90) if auto1 == true and text >= 32 and text <= 64 then screen.drawText(22, 26, "64") elseif auto1 == true and text >= 64 and text <=96 then screen.drawText(22, 26, "96") elseif auto1 == true and text >= 96 and text <=128 then screen.drawText(17, 26, "128") elseif auto1 == true and text >= 128 and text <=160 then screen.drawText(17, 26, "160") -- elseif auto1 == true and text >= 96 and text <=112 then screen.drawText(17, 26, "112") --elseif auto1 == true and text >= 112 and text <=128 then screen.drawText(17, 26, "128") --elseif auto1 == true and text >= 128 and text <=150 then screen.drawText(17, 26, "150") elseif text1 <= 100 then screen.drawText(22, 26, text1) else screen.drawText(17, 26, text1) end
if zoomin then screen.setColor(0,100,15,255) screen.drawText(27, 7, "+") elseif auto1 == false then screen.setColor(0,100,15,90) screen.drawText(27, 7, "+") end if zoomout then screen.setColor(0,100,15,255) screen.drawText(27, 20, "-") elseif auto1 == false then screen.setColor(0,100,15,90) screen.drawText(27, 20, "-") end
if rdown then screen.setColor(0,100,15,255) screen.drawText(7, 1, "+") else screen.setColor(0,100,15,90) screen.drawText(7, 1, "+") end if rup then screen.setColor(0,100,15,255) screen.drawText(7, 5, "-") else screen.setColor(0,100,15,90) screen.drawText(7, 5, "-") end end

microprocessor_definition.name: Seat W/S + Depth Comp Mixer (to Clutches MC)

object.script:
local gB, gN, sB, sN, pN, pB = input.getBool, input.getNumber, output.setBool, output.setNumber, property.getNumber, property.getBool
local deltas = {0, 0, 0, 0} local axes = {0, 0, 0, 0} local labels = {{"Axis 1 [a]/[d] Sensitivity (%)", "Axis 2 [w]/[s] Sensitivity (%)", "Axis 3 [left]/[right] Sensitivity (%)", "Axis 4 [up]/[down] Sensitivity (%)"}, {"Axis 1 [a]/[d] Mode", "Axis 2 [w]/[s] Mode", "Axis 3 [left]/[right] Mode", "Axis 4 [up]/[down] Mode"}} local properties = {{0, 0, 0, 0}, {false, false, false, false}} local init = true
function onTick() if init then for i = 1, 4 do properties[1][i] = pN(labels[1][i]) / 100 properties[2][i] = pB(labels[2][i]) end init = false end for i = 1, 6 do sB(i,gB(i)) end for i = 1, 4 do local axis = gN(i) local delta = axis - deltas[i] deltas[i] = axis if (delta > 0.0001 and axis > 0) or delta > 0.02 or axis > 0.99 then axes[i] = lerp(axes[i], 1, properties[1][i]) sN(i, axes[i]) elseif (delta < -0.0001 and axis < 0) or delta < -0.02 or axis < -0.99 then axes[i] = lerp(axes[i], -1, properties[1][i]) sN(i, axes[i]) elseif not properties[2][i] then axes[i] = lerp(axes[i], 0, properties[1][i]) sN(i, axes[i]) end end end
function lerp(a,b,t) return a + (b-a) * t * t end
